            <p>The <span class="font-weight-700">Yamaha R15</span> flaunts its fully-faired, aerodynamic look inspired by Yamaha's R-series superbikes. Its sharp LED headlamps, sporty fairing, and crouched riding posture make it look track-ready.</p>
